{
  "stem": "15082.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in 1937, Czechoslovakian Jews that ran away from Hitler were coming across to our-- the whole area there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, in the small town, where would they come first?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to shul, to see Jewish families, and to see where they can be taken, and what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would tell their stories and the atrocities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would listen in as a young kid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] even the older people did not want to believe the stories that I head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just like they tried to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not hear them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When I look back now, how could that had happened?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to hear what they were telling us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's why I'm so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bent on, and the Holocaust, has to be talked about, repeated, really, because some of the Jews in those days couldn't believe that something terrible like this could happen.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these people came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were barefoot in the coldest day, I saw them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With clothes that was all ripped already, because they were probably wandering for months and months until they reached this town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, our house was a very, very hospitable house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother never knew who would come home Friday night for supper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If my father would go to shul, and there was a stranger or somebody, we would always have strange people for supper in our house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these people came to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I recall as a child sitting around, you know, they're telling their stories, and their plight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is the first time that I became aware of what's going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were compassionate.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
